How to set up
=============

You need Node.js in order to run krowdf server.

- Launch your terminal and go into 'server' sub-directory
- Run the command: npm install
- Modify local.json for your needs
- Run the command: node main

Design
======

If you want to use your own design for server website, just modify index.html as you need.
The internal main js file use Angular.js in order to display data, and Socket.io for getting datas from the server.

Read the Angular.js doc and the example index.html in order to create your own design easily.

PS: Just don't forget the <script data-main="entry" src="/require.min.js"></script> in your page.
